high_descs: Head rotate and walk towards the shelf.
Turn right and pick the pen from the rack.
Head rotate to the plate rack.
Pick the plate along with the knife from the rack.
Turn left and walk towards the plate.
Turn left to the desk.
Place the plate with the knife in the desk.
anns.task_desc: To place the pen with the knife in the desk.

high_descs: Turn towards left and enter into a room and then take a right turn and reach the last shelf.
Take the pen from the rack.
Make a little bit move to the right side and reach the first plate rack.
Put the pen on the plate which is kept in the rack.
Take the plate along with the pen.
Turn back and walk towards the desk.
Put the plate with pen on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place the pen on the plate on the desk.

high_descs: Head toward the shelf, then turn right to the Wooden table.
Pick the pen from the table.
Go near to the plate.
Take a plate from the table.
Take a plate and pen then turn around.
Go straight to reach the desk.
Put the plate and pen on the top of the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put pen and plate on the top on the desk.
